      Alter a film, book, or song title, or a common phrase, by adding, subtracting, or changing one letter.

      %a.font20.pull-right{"data-toggle" => "modal", :href => "#howToPlay"} 
        How to play.
        %i.fa.fa-info-circle
  .col-md-12
    #howToPlay.modal.fade
      .modal-dialog.modal-lg
        .modal-content
          .modal-header
            %button.close{"aria-hidden" => "true", "data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} Ã—
            %h4.modal-title How To Play
          .modal-body
            %p
              The premise of the game is that you alter a film, book, or song title, or a common phrase, by adding, subtracting, or changing
              %strong ONE
              letter.  Now you've created a new title or phrase. The challenge is to construct a clever description for what you've just created.
            %hr
            .row
              .col-md-4
                .highest-rated-container.pad2.panel.panel-default
                  %strong Add-a-letter example:
                  %ol
                    %li Baker's Dozen
                    %li Add an "R"
                    %li
                      = "Ba<strong>R</strong>ker's Dozen".html_safe
                  %strong New Description:
                  %br
                  A litter of 13 puppies

              .col-md-4
                .weeks-highest-rated.pad2.panel.panel-default
                  %strong Delete-a-letter example:
                  %ol
                    %li Big Lebowski.
                    %li Delete the 'g'.
                    %li Bi Lebowski.
                  %strong New Description:
                  %br
                  Polish immigrant struggles with his sexuality
              .col-md-4
                .pad2.panel.panel-default
                  %strong Change-a-letter example:
                  %ol
                    %li Lust for Life
                    %li Change first "L" to a "D"
                    %li= "<strong>D</strong>ust for Life".html_safe
                  %strong New Description:
                  %br
                  Roomba Guarantee

          .modal-footer
            %button.btn.btn-default{"data-dismiss" => "modal", :type => "button"} Close